 \section*{*Branch and Bound Method }

\paragraph{Heuristic and metaheuristic algorithms are used when problem becomes too large for exact method. Exact method is complicated than heuristic method. Exact method give solution of large scale problem instances in manageable times.}                                                       \paragraph{                          Genetic algorithm is used more than other method to solve assignment problem.	Currently many mathematicians evaluate assignment problem by using varius techniques such as Fuzzy logic, Machine learning, genetic algorithm, Matlab programming. Currently Mathematicians also works on  quadratic assignment problem.}
\section*{1) Quadratic Assignment Problem (QAP) : }
Quadratic assignment problem was introduced  by  Koopmans and Beckmann in 1957. QAP is one of the fundamental combinatorial optimization problem. QAP has many applications in real life such as scheduling, production, computer manufacture, chemistry, facility location, communication and other field. 
\section*{2) Assignment problem by genetic algorithm:}  
Genetic algorithms are a class of algorithms designed to explore a large search space and finite optimal solutions by mimicking evolution and natural selection. In a genetic algorithm three operators are apply on population of string (called chromosomes or the genotype of the genome) to approach better solution.This three operators are 1) Cross-over   2)  Mutation   3) Selection
\section*{3)Fuzzy Assignment Problem (FAP): }
Fuzzy logic is a form of many-valued logic in which the truth values of variables may be any real number between o and 1. It is employed to handle the concept of partial truth. Hungarian method is used to solve FAP by using ranking function for fuzzy costs.
\section*{4) Assignment problem by using machine learning: }
Over the last few year use of machine learning in various field is popular and also necessary.  Machine learning(ML) is the study of computer algorithms that can improve automatically through experience and by the use of data. The study of  mathematical optimization delivers methods, theory and application domains to the ield o machine learning.\\



